query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(s t tq) NoHashJoin(s t tq q) */ select count(*)
from tag AS t
inner join site AS s
on t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-identity',
'google-maps-markers',
'internet-explorer-8') AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND tq.site_id = s.site_id
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10;
